{"tid":1690911,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[行動post ] 要全港大罷工 只要搞掂運輸業就得","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T17:14:53.000Z","uid":54243,"like":81,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"47ec37db682efddb8ff7819b101ffe7bc0ae9747","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"大部分香港人都唔係自己果區返工 甚至要過海<br />\n無車既話 唔通你游水過海咩<br />\n全港黨鐵 巴士 小巴司機一齊大罷工 全港癱瘓九成<br />\n連機場員工都返唔到工 癱瘓埋機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然d 司機問 你養我呀？ <br />\n係呀 我養你<br />\n香港人出名錢多 d 錢與其去落廣告 倒不如去資助肯罷工既人 <br />\n只要有一筆夠大既錢去養佢地 佢地就可以安心罷工<br />\n當然要時間籌旗 亦要有公信力既人做眾籌手 我首選攬炒巴<br />\n當然而家係初步階段 詳細要再商量 但大罷工要時間籌備 而家就要開始<br />\n只要夠齊心 就唔怕秋後 特別係司機呢個行業無咩後生仔入行 如果再大炒人既 真係幫手攬炒交通"},{"pid":"6abe713901c6d1c344484f1070b53bbbc8cd826a","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"D 錢可以夠養呢班司機一年既 我相信佢地肯罷工"},{"pid":"9f2adfa035f90abc9d4e0dd58ba47e879123e059","tid":1690911,"uid":44813,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30f26b6740e64eeb342c027c7e5d20aa08a1ea2","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9f2adfa035f90abc9d4e0dd58ba47e879123e059","tid":1690911,"uid":44813,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:50:58.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"咁你有咩建議去發動大罷工<br />\n唔係冒犯 真心求教<br />\n希望你有幫助到革命既意見可以分享下"},{"pid":"1d0aeb1868152302b5ddcf4b0372dfd47f3401af","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"有咩意見都提出黎"},{"pid":"52615070193e8408491ad4a2f1fe177f61655469","tid":1690911,"uid":266676,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"罷工一定要有罷工基金<br />\n太多人係有返工先有糧出<br />\n如果可以罷工拎準貼 罷工人數應該會多d"},{"pid":"c5fdaf9ccb26ba248827cee6716aa0bae9f2d5a4","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52615070193e8408491ad4a2f1fe177f61655469","tid":1690911,"uid":266676,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"罷工一定要有罷工基金<br />\n太多人係有返工先有糧出<br />\n如果可以罷工拎準貼 罷工人數應該會多d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:19:05.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n所以要眾籌一個基金 學外國工會咁<br />\n有錢維持生活開支"},{"pid":"5a20259c174c48584bc471280b61497eeeec7e6c","tid":1690911,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"唔要 : 推！<br />\n試著說 : 我要罷工！<br />\n將罷工融入日常同口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要罷工！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！</span><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b13027a9b97dc158e01566bfa7d4bc99fdf1e","tid":1690911,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a20259c174c48584bc471280b61497eeeec7e6c","tid":1690911,"uid":263622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"唔要 : 推！<br />\n試著說 : 我要罷工！<br />\n將罷工融入日常同口號<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要罷工！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！</span><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"